text: Kamaruddin Ahmed is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Dinajpur-1. ==Career== Ahmed was elected to parliament from Dinajpur-1 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Kamaruddin Ahmed
